      <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"9417 characters\">        Laravel Jetstream provides a beautiful, robust starting point for your next Laravel application. Laravel is designed<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\n</span></span>
      <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"9417 characters\">        to help you build your application using a development environment that is simple, powerful, and enjoyable. We believe<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\n</span></span>
      <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"9417 characters\">        you should love expressing your creativity through programming, so we have spent time carefully crafting the Laravel<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\n</span></span>
      <span class=sf-dump-str title=\"9417 characters\">        ecosystem to be a breath of fresh air. We hope you love it.<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\n</span></span>
